"     Deputy Editor",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?35/32/36361/contributors\">",
"     Brian C Downey, MD, FACC",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
